HEADWORD: Photobacterium
<hw>Pho`to*bac*te"ri*um</hw>
<pr>(f⟦omac⟧`t⟦osl⟧*b⟦acr⟧k*t⟦emac⟧"r⟦esl⟧*⟦ucr⟧m)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
